zh","original_name":"江火澄燃","overview":"","popularity":0.0554,"poster_path":"/f7C4jxR3uleehd6ZK3JJxKNsUdJ.jpg","production_companies":[],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","name":"China"}],"seasons":[{"air_date":"2025-12-15","episode_count":20,"id":489110,"name":"Season 1","overview":"","poster_path":null,"season_number":1,"vote_average":0}],"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"Mandarin","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话"}],"status":"Ended","tagline":"","type":"Scripted","vote_average":0,"vote_count":0}},"person_1230286_translations":{"at":1773688730436,"data":{"id":1230286,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Marg Downey","primary":true}}]}},"person_1231106_translations":{"at":1773688730508,"data":{"id":1231106,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Stephen's best known for his role as 'Brax' in the long running Australian serial drama, 'Home & Away'. He's appeared in various other Australian Film, Television and Theatre productions and most recently worked on Brett Ratner's, 'Hercules', along side Dwayne Johnson, John Hurt and Ian McShane. Stephen grew up in Dubbo in Central Western New South Wales, worked as a Jackaroo on a large scale sheep & cattle station west of Bourke and graduated from the University of Newcastle with a degree in Communications. His passion before acting was Rugby Union where he played at First Grade and Representative levels throughout his schooling, university and adult life.","name":"Stephen Peacocke","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"Stephen ist vor allem für seine Rolle als „Brax“ in der langjährigen australischen Serie „Home & Away“ bekannt.  Er trat in verschiedenen anderen australischen Film-, Fernseh- und Theaterproduktionen auf und arbeitete zuletzt an der Seite von Dwayne Johnson, John Hurt und Ian McShane an „Hercules“ von Brett Ratner.  Stephen wuchs in Dubbo im zentralen Westen von New South Wales auf, arbeitete als Jackaroo auf einer großen Schaf- und Rinderfarm westlich von Bourke und schloss sein Studium der Kommunikationswissenschaften an der University of Newcastle ab.  Seine Leidenschaft zu der Schauspielerei wurde an Rugby Union geweckt, wo er während seiner Schul-, Universitäts- und Erwachsenenzeit in der ersten Klasse und in der Repräsentantenklasse spielte.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"斯蒂芬最出名的是他在长期播出的澳大利亚连续剧《Home & Away》中扮演的“Brax”。他曾出演过其他各种澳大利亚电影、电视和戏剧作品，最近与道恩·强森、约翰·赫特和伊恩·麦克肖恩一起参与了布雷特·拉特纳的《大力神》的制作。斯蒂芬在新南威尔士州中西部的达博长大，在伯克以西的一个大型牛羊站担任Jackaroo，毕业于纽卡斯尔大学，获得传播学学位。在演戏之前，他的热情是橄榄球联盟，在他的学校、大学和成年生活中，他都参加了一年级和代表级别的比赛。","name":"斯蒂芬·皮科克","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SG","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"斯蒂芬·皮科克","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"GR","iso_639_1":"el","name":"ελληνικά","english_name":"Greek","data":{"biography":"","name":"Στίφεν Πίκοκ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"סטיבן פיקוק","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IN","iso_639_1":"hi","name":"हिन्दी","english_name":"Hindi","data":{"biography":"","name":"स्टीफ़न पीकोक","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"スティーヴン・ピーコック","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Стивен Пикок","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"สตีเฟน พีค็อก","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Стівен Пікок","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"斯蒂芬最出名的是他在長期播出的澳大利亞聯續劇《Home & Away》中扮演的“Brax”。他曾出演過其他各種澳大利亞電影、電視和戲劇作品，最近與道恩·強森、約翰·赫特和伊恩·麥克肖恩一起參與了佈雷特·拉特納的《大力戰神》的製作。斯蒂芬在新南威爾士州中西部的達博長大，在伯克以西的一個大型牛羊站擔任 Jackaroo，畢業於紐卡斯爾大學，獲得傳播學學位。在演戲之前，他的熱情是橄欖球聯盟，在他的學校、大學和成年生活中，他都參加了一年級和代表級別的比賽。","name":"斯蒂芬·皮科克","primary":false}}]}},"person_541233_translations":{"at":1773688730595,"data":{"id":541233,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Bonnie Law Ming-Chu","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"罗明珠","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"羅明珠","primary":true}}]}},"person_1350166_translations":{"at":1773688730893,"data":{"id":1350166,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"李雨阳（Eddie Li Yu Yeung），男，1979年3月30日出生，香港无线电视演员。\n\n2003年于无线电视剧集《当四叶草碰上剑尖时》初登荧幕，他饰演一个富家子弟，认为自己拥有很多金钱。","name":"李雨阳","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Eddie Li Yu-Yeung","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"李雨陽（Eddie Li Yu Yeung），男，1979 年 3 月 30 日出生，香港無線電視演員。\n\n2003 年於無線電視劇集《當四葉草碰上劍尖時》初登熒幕，他飾演一個富家子弟，認為自己擁有很多金錢。","name":"李雨陽","primary":true}}]}},"tv_263048_detail_vi-VN":{"at":1773688732633,"data":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/zBgOoOIfVdPbIUkaT9lxthcsUAZ.jpg","created_by":[],"episode_run_time":[],"first_air_date":"2025-12-04","genres":[{"id":18,"name":"Phim Chính Kịch"}],"homepage":"https://v.qq.com/x/cover/mzc00200djd8qu9.html","id":263048,"in_production":false,"languages":["zh"],"last_air_date":"2025-12-15","last_episode_to_air":{"id":6751212,"name":"Episode 30","overview":"","vote_av