":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"藤井幸代（日语：藤井 ゆきよ／ふじい ゆきよ Fujii Yukiyo，1985年5月8日—）为日本女性声优、演员。隶属于青二制作，神奈川县出身。身高169cm、血型为O型。\n\n兴趣是篮球、足球、料理、读书。\n\n进入声优业界前以藤井幸代之名活动，曾经从事舞台照明技术者工作（持有照明技术者技能检定2级）。2007年先后参加PRINCESS PINKY、日本国际小姐选拔。\n\nAOI CORPORATION所属时改为现在艺名，除演出戏剧外亦开始声优生涯。2011年4月移籍至青二制作。\n\n剧场版动画《帕蒂玛的颠倒世界》为初次主演。","name":"藤井幸代","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"藤井幸代為日本女性聲優、演員。出生於島根縣，成長於神奈川縣，所屬公司為青二製作。","name":"藤井幸代","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Yukiyo Fujii (藤井 ゆきよ, Fujī Yukiyo, nacida el 8 de mayo de 1985) es un actor y actriz de doblaje (seiyuu) japonesa nacida en la prefectura de Shimane, y criada en la prefectura de Kanagawa. Pertenece a Aoni Production.","name":"Yukiyo Fujii","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"후지이 유키요","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"藤井ゆきよ","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"SA","iso_639_1":"ar","name":"العربية","english_name":"Arabic","data":{"biography":"","name":"يوكيو فوجي","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"יוקיו פוג'י","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"GR","iso_639_1":"el","name":"ελληνικά","english_name":"Greek","data":{"biography":"","name":"Γιουκίγιο Φούτζιι","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"ยูคิโยะ ฟูจิ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Юкиё Фудзии","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ю